data.description: Welcome to your new home located in the highly sought out neighborhood of Mimosa Bay!! This community features a clubhouse, fitness center, pool, playground, tennis courts, walking trails, boat ramp and boat dock. Conveniently located between Wilmington and Jacksonville and just minutes from Camp Lejuene, Stone Bay and local beaches! Once you enter the property you will find an open concept layout perfect for entertaining. The large living room opens to a spacious kitchen that features a beautiful island surrounded by upgraded cabinetry and granite countertops. The eat in kitchen nook finishes off this space with the perfect place to enjoy a coffee and your breakfast. The first-floor master suite is nicely sized with a walk-in closet and en-suite bathroom complete with soaking tube and walk in shower. The two additional bedrooms are located on the other side of the home with a full bathroom conveniently located in between the two. Last but not least located up the stairs off the laundry room is a large bonus room perfect for an office or game room. The fenced in backyard features a covered patio perfect for grilling out on those beautiful Carolina nights. Don't miss your opportunity to call this great home and neighborhood your own!!
